<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      .header {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #2d3748;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .content {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #4a5568;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        background-color: #3182ce;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #a0aec0;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body style="background-color: #edf2f7; padding: 20px;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        Termsheet from Longleaf Lending
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= @lead.name %>,</p>
        <p>Thank you for your interest in Longleaf Lending. Attached is the termsheet based on the information you provided.</p>
        <p>Please review the termsheet and let us know if you have any questions.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        Longleaf Lending Team</p>
        <%= link_to "Visit Our Website", home_url, class: "bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded" %>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        &copy; <%= Date.today.year %> Longleaf Lending. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
